### Test Phone Verification Flow
# This file contains HTTP requests to test the phone verification flow
# You can use REST Client extension in VS Code to execute these requests

### 1. Send OTP to a user
POST http://localhost:8081/user/send-phone-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "YOUR_USER_ID_HERE"
}

### 2. Verify OTP
POST http://localhost:8081/user/verify-phone-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "YOUR_USER_ID_HERE",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### 3. Resend OTP
POST http://localhost:8081/user/resend-phone-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "YOUR_USER_ID_HERE"
}
